<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//VoiceXML Forum//DTD XHTML+Voice 1.2//EN"
	"http://www.voicexml.org/specs/multimodal/x+v/12/dtd/xhtml+voice12.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:vxml="http://www.w3.org/2001/vxml"
      xmlns:ev="http://www.w3.org/2001/xml-events"
      xmlns:xv="http://www.voicexml.org/2002/xhtml+voice">
<head>
  <title>Vox ACSS Test: pause-after &lt;keyword&gt;</title>

  <vxml:form id="vox">
   <vxml:block><vxml:prompt src="#text"/></vxml:block>
  </vxml:form>
  
  <style type="text/css">
  #p1 {
    pause-after: none;
  }
  #p2 {
    pause-after: x-weak;
  }
  #p3 {
    pause-after: weak;
  }
  #p4 {
    pause-after: medium;
  }
  #p5 {
    pause-after: strong;
  }
  #p6 {
    pause-after: x-strong;
  }
  </style>
</head>

<body ev:event="load" ev:handler="#vox" id="text">
<h1>
  pause-after &lt;keyword&gt;
</h1>
<p id="p1">No pause after this paragraph.</p>
<div>Done.</div>
<p id="p2">x-weak pause after this paragraph.</p>
<div>Done.</div>
<p id="p3">weak pause after this paragraph.</p>
<div>Done.</div>
<p id="p4">medium pause after this paragraph.</p>
<div>Done.</div>
<p id="p5">strong pause after this paragraph.</p>
<div>Done.</div>
<p id="p6">x-strong pause after this paragraph.</p>
<div>Done.</div>
</body>
</html>
